summary:
I am currently a third year student in International Relations and Organizations at Leiden University, in The Hague (Netherlands). I am currently finishing my studies with a smester abroad in Egypt, at the American Univeristy of Cairo. 

Before starting a Masters' degree in International Development, I would like to gain more professional experience, either through internships or jobs, from September 2023 onwards. As of now, I am considering a career in International Development either in a French or European embassy, international organization (WHO, UNICEF), or in an NGO.
